HelpTooltip:
Calculates the differences between the first input and the second input/s and outputs the distance value in an array of floats.

First Input port and Second Input port connect to a Feature Extractor or a Datatype node. Both inputs
must be of the same type. Live Data Out port connects to a Serial Vector feature extractor.
PortTooltip: Connect a Feature Extractor or Data Type node
Connect to Serial Vector. Outputs an array of float values.

tips: Float value/s of distance between inputs
